snippet.textDisplay: The Mugshot scene. I am the one that gave it to him. I used to work for Memphis Police and I got the original before the negative was destroyed since charges were dropped against him . Then in 91 I became a IATSE stagehand for Local #589 in Jackson Ms. and Ozzy came to town and I took the mugshot to get it signed. Well a roadie saw it and it got back to Ozzy and he sent his assistant out to get me and he asked if he could have it and I said it is the only one I have so he asked me can I make a copy which I did and sent to him. This is the copy you see in the video.. Proud moment for me now
